<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시글 확인 웹페이지</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>게시글 확인 및 수정/삭제 웹페이지</h1>
    <form method="post" action="/article/modify/<%=article.article_id%>">
        제목 : <br>
        <input name="title" type="text" id="title" value="<%=article.title %>"/><br>
        내용 : <br>
        <textarea id="contents" name = "contents" style="height: 500px;"><%=article.contents %></textarea><br>
        게시여부 : <br>
        <select id="display" name="display">
            <option value="9">선택</option>
            <option vaule="1">게시함</option>
            <option value="0">게시안함</option>
        </select>
        <br>

        <input type="submit" value="수정"/>
        <input type="button" value="삭제"/>
        <input type="button" value="목록"/>
        
    </form>
</body>
</html>